reviewText: My Husband was so happy with this order--hard to find titles! Thanks

I am so happy they released dvds of Space Goofs!!!! A brilliant cartoon that as a child i was so obsessed with i have an entire notebook of drawings with them and movie poster parodies of them. It always will have a special place in my heart because it is one of the many shows that will always remind me of my childhood and will always make me happy. This show rocks!!!!!!!
